      <subsection id="H3A33D84B7BBC4F72BF563795FB005078">
        <enum>(c)</enum>
        <header>Effective
			 date</header>
        <text>The amendments made by this section shall apply to property
			 originally placed in service on or after January 1, 2013.</text>
